flowRoot.flowPara: CryptoParty events are taking place everywhere in the world. We're going to host one in Townsville and want you to come! Tell us you're interested & we'lll keep you updated.
We're looking for expressions of interest! CryptoParty is free, public, and fun. Everyone can learn it -- the only thing you need is a laptop or a smartphone!
Attend a CryptoParty to learn or teach how to encrypt emails, chats and data and how to stay anonymous online. Everyone has the right to have privacy. Everyone can learn it!
CryptoParty is a global, decentralized initiative to introduce the most basic cryptography programs (VPN, Tor, GPG, etc) and fundamental concepts of their operation to the general public.
